---
title: Garlic Lime Chicken Fajitas with Pickled Onion & Lime Crema
description: Ready for your 5-second meditation? Okay: Close your eyes. Hear the sizzle. Smell the caramelized peppers and onions. Feel the warm steam hit your face. Picture the jealous stares knowing that you, as usual, ordered the best dish on the menu. Yes, we’re talking fajitas, people! Now for the real moment of zen: This restaurant staple is (gasp) better—and even more satisfying—when you make it yourself! Especially when tangy, garlicky chicken, zingy pickled onion, and cooling lime crema are involved.
